          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJo6lUl_FsuwbC03CWHfIPxy6t-LAU5ztcVlTWTOKv0qlz4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I've asked this pharmacy repeatedly to stop calling me to refill a prescription.  They even called once, I declined, and then they refilled the script anyhow.  Then called me repeatedly to pick up the medication.  Every time they call I ask them to stop calling as I've transferred my prescription due to their constant harassment.  The representative on the phone suggested I would need to speak with the manager of the store to cease the calls.  As of now, I've logged in and simply changed my phone number.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZMFJ6VmtkRXR5VVRCUFoyVlFYMkpsYVdZMFlYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa855bcbe1f5a62ec!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnY0RzVkdEtyUTBPZ2VQX2JlaWY0YXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "9 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-09-01T19:00:35+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Tito Promo",
          "rating": 3,
          "contributor_id": "101237276904712630899",
          "user_review_count": 32,
          "user_photo_count": 3,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRdr-NiRoYEGpjQGgeUBhkJaeIe04Yw1j7AewjMMj0ML3N2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Gets a \"3\" rating for two reasons [it could prob hike to a \"4\", but not yet], two positives:\n(1.) Their late night hours. It's one of the few chain places/pharmacies that have remained 24hrs in this city. A rare find, especially on the East side of Manhattan. KEEP IT THAT WAY!\n(2.) This Duane Reade is massive and stacked with goods. Has a pretty good selection of everything, including refrigerated/frozen foods.\n\nNow to the ugly part:\n(1.) The pharmacy is SUPER SLOW. If you have to go there, especially late, plan on some wait time for your meds. I'd suggest calling ahead making sure they are ready for pickup or checking on the website/app (but this proved not to be reliable for me). Duane Reade, in my view, has some of the quickest pharmacies in New York --but this one-- not so much.\n(2.) In the middle of a heatwave, and their A/C was OFF!! The staff there was sweating bullets and so were the customers. I went late, but can't imagine if that's the case during the day. Terrible way to proceed or enthuse people to keep buying. I just wanted to run out of there, but couldn't, because my script took an extra 30mins to be filled.\n\nThis Duane Reade has potential. Now, live up to it!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkRVdsRmFTVTVHZW0xbWVuUjFhM1J4U0dKcVRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa855bcbe1f5a62ec!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkdEWlFaSU5Gem1menR1a3RxSGJqTmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "10 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-08-04T06:51:04+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Miranda Nykolyn",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "110354744389816050018",
          "user_review_count": 6,
