          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWDAJvHgDgsq6xcaBd_YPOoT_mFblSD4kdfJmoO3k0lnmmAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I\u2019ve had consistently poor experiences with this pharmacy. They frequently mishandle my prescriptions \u2014 from not ordering my medication on time to making the pickup process unnecessarily difficult. Despite multiple attempts to resolve these issues, staff remain unhelpful and dismissive. They also refuse to honor my valid savings card, which has added to the frustration. I\u2019ve wasted countless hours here and received little to no support or accountability. This has been one of the most unreliable and unprofessional pharmacies I\u2019ve dealt with",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxR1EzcGlZbVpWV2tnM1dFMUZNWFppVVc1b1owRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa855bcbe1f5a62ec!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOi1GQ3piYmZVWkg3WE1FMXZiUW5oZ0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
