          "description": "This is the closest pharmacy I have to get my prescription. There\u2019s this man that works at the pharmacy. I believe his name is Daniel, but I could be wrong. Every time I get him in person or on the phone, he gives me the biggest attitude and almost screams at me. Today, was my last straw! For this man to be a pharmacist and to talk to patients this way, it\u2019s unacceptable. Especially when every other person that works in thar  pharmacy has been nothing but  sweet . This man should not be working with customers. I never seen him a good mood or treat anymore in that matter, It alway feel like we are bother him and we are stupid human beings.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SM1NreHJOVU5FY1U5d2RrSTNUbmhaYlZOV1FYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa855bcbe1f5a62ec!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmR3SkxrNUNEcU9wdkI3TnhZbVNWQXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
