          "description": "Worst picking up my medicine. My dentist sent my toothpaste to this pharmacy in December. No notification at all till I moved to NJ. I came to pick up in March, lunchtime, the pharmacy closed till 2pm\u2026.When they came back to work, they need to log in, clean stuff first\u2026..Finally my turn, find my prescription and toothpaste, ask me to wait for 15 mins to get my medicine. I came here a lot before and always felt good, but today\u2026\u2026.cannot be worse.",
